The paper deals with representing, learning, and reasoning with preferences, which is a central area of study in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of deep neural networks to learn a metric function also falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of CP-nets, which are commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR) and decision making (cs.DS). Finally, the paper mentions the use of siamese networks, which are commonly used in natural language processing (cs.CL).
